節目作討論都好 大家有noise同參與度"},{"pid":"5adbdd62d94bda58192e0d86b5f80c129e32601c","tid":1428793,"uid":92340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"同意就比正評<br />\n唔同意就由佢沉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都幾識玩"},{"pid":"088d672b842552878d951608523f8761c6909ecc","tid":1428793,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"不如兩至三年一次"},{"pid":"4ec7096f370ba1af2e76c1d795fa245d6729f37e","tid":1428793,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e8fa77d51cab2d627efef7552f69e99e5f5becd3","tid":1428793,"uid":20916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ef346da2f3ff718187ad7456a7143a1ea31017a","tid":1428793,"uid":159016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:11:18.000Z","msg":"傻仔 你同共產黨玩政治宣傳<br />\n你食得屎啦 <br />\n共產黨開始識得控制宣傳工具洗腦時<br />\n連你阿爺都沒出世<br />\n講平反暴動定性同防止扣帽仲搞笑<br />\n你不如叫佢平反64"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"呢排好多人指返啲舊方法出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deecd5b3c5c41a055c44430dae15687285584f8d","tid":1428793,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"237e194074b3351528761c794a55f8aa3095b5e2","tid":1428793,"uid":44870,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:08:44.000Z","msg":"兩至三個星期一次, 咪玩啦, 咩熱度都冇哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:17:09.000Z","msg":"係可以斟酌嘅 但我覺得而家真係密集咗啲 好似以今個星期為例就有8月5，9，10同11 。仲未計突然圍狗署嗰啲"},{"pid":"6800d2ea05b61a3df23b4010f26ce0cbc994bb04","tid":1428793,"uid":173612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5adbdd62d94bda58192e0d86b5f80c129e32601c","tid":1428793,"uid":92340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"同意就比正評<br />\n唔同意就由佢沉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都幾識玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi